result.adr_address: 2/F, Parekh House, 63 Wyndham St, Central, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 2/F, Parekh House, 63 Wyndham St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Casa Lisboa

reviews.text: Kind service and delicious dishes. Does not disappoint. The Serradura dessert is to die for! So good! I recommend!

If you are in HK on a weekend looking for a magnificent brunch far from the madding crowds, this is for you!  A whole bunch of starters, main, dessert and coffee included.  Garlic octopus is awesome as is the duck rice.

Amazing outstanding
We were very lucky, we arrived very early for lunchtime.  As 1st guests, the Chef Fabio came to our table and explained everything.
We've got the crab, codfish cakes, piri piri chicken, codfish and amazing desserts.
The service was excellent.  We'll return many times from now on.
Congratulations to the whole team and special thanks to Fabio.
Two very enjoyable dinners back to back. That’s how good it was; I came back the next night! Follow the staff’s recommendations and your tummy will thank you.
The best Portuguese restaurant in HK. Always a pleasure to be back. Great food, great staff and impressive wine list. Couldn't recommend it most. Well done
